# User Prompt Template

```text
Analyze the following RSS item.

Title:
{{title}}

Source:
{{source}}

URL:
{{url}}

Published At:
{{published_at}}

Author:
{{author}}

Content:
{{content}}

Write summary, positive_reasons, and negative_reasons in {{output_language}}.
